ton\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104kjr1676877187333.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kjr1676877187333.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kjr1676877187333.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"kno1665702715145\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Window property of a form or application shell that determines whether the window can be resized at runtime.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kno1665702715145__section_w1133ab1b5b1_w1134ab1b5_w1135ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"kno1665702715145__table_d10970e1_d10971e1_d10972e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"kno1665702715145__table_d10970e1_d10971e1_d10972e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"kno1665702715145__table_d10970e1_d10971e1_d10972e1__entry__2\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kno1665702715145__table_d10970e1_d10971e1_d10972e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">True</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kno1665702715145__table_d10970e1_d10971e1_d10972e1__entry__2\">Window can be resized by dragging the window\n                        borders. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kno1665702715145__table_d10970e1_d10971e1_d10972e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kno1665702715145__table_d10970e1_d10971e1_d10972e1__entry__2\">Window cannot be resized. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kno1665702715145__section_vwd_kgl_4wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d749280e100\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"kno1665702715145__table_d10973e1_d10974e1_d10975e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dynamic? </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">No </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dependencies:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> For application shells, if\n                           <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Resizable</span> is <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code> ,\n                           <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Dialog Type</span> is set to <code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code> , and\n                        vice versa. <p class=\"p\">For form components, if <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Resizable</span> is\n                              <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>, <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Window Type</span> cannot be\n                           set to <code class=\"ph codeph\">Dialog</code> or <code class=\"ph codeph\">Tab</code>, and vice\n                           versa.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kno1665702715145__section_pbl_lgl_4wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d749280e167\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"kno1665702715145__ul_fn1_ngl_4wb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kno1665702715145__li_d40511e1_d40512e1_d40513e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yye1705472567076.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yye1705472567076.html\" title=\"An application shell is the first object that is executed when a Windows or character mode application is started. It determines how the application is initialized and the first form component that is displayed.\">Application Shells for Desktop Applications</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kno1665702715145__li_d40514e1_d40515e1_d40516e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"usl1704692305727.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/usl1704692305727.html\" title=\"Form components provide the user interface for Uniface desktop applications. They are always executed on the client system and can be modal (form retains focus until it is closed) or non-modal (users can switch focus to other forms).\">Forms</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/eoe1665702580713.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Dialog Window</a><p>A dialog window is a modal, non-resizable window used to display forms as dialog boxes, which is typically used to display or retrieve a limited amount of information. It is defined by setting the window property Window Type to Dialog.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dto1665702580637.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Window Type (WindowType)</a><p>Window property of a form that determines the type of window used to display the form. One of: Normal | Dialog | Primary | Secondary | Contained | Popup</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3608441\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3608441\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Resizable (CanResize) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Window property of a form or application shell that determines whether the window can be resized at runtime. Value Description True Window can be resized by dragging the window borders. False Window cannot be resized. Usage Dynamic? No Dependencies: For application shells, if Resizable is True , Dialog Type is set to False , and vice versa. For form components, if Resizable is True , Window Type cannot be set to Dialog or Tab , and vice versa. Applies To Application Shells for Desktop Applications Forms Related Links Dialog Window A dialog window is a modal, non-resizable window used to display forms as dialog boxes, which is typically used to display or retrieve a limited amount of information. It is defined by setting the window property Window Type to Dialog. Window Type (WindowType) Window property of a form that determines the type of window used to display the form. One of: Normal | Dialog | Primary | Secondary | Contained | Popup Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}